<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.9.7">
<l>puḷḷiṉai vāypiḷan tuporu mākari kompocittu</l>
<l>kaḷḷa<supplied>c</supplied>ca kaṭutait takaru māṇikka  māmalaiyai</l>
<l>teḷḷaru vikoḻik kumtiru māliruñ cōlainiṉṟa</l>
<l>vaḷḷalai vāṇuta lāḷvaṇaṅ kittoḻa vallaḷkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is the girl with the bright forehead [so] fervent to worship, adoring</l>
<l>The liberal [lord] who stands in Tirumāliruñcōlai where clear waterfalls flow,</l>
<l>That great, dark emerald mountain who kicked the demon cart,</l>
<l>Having split the bird’s mouth [and] broken the tusk of a huge, war elephant?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
